{"id": "1359063007514066964", "channel_id": "1358673487673167942", "type": 19, "author_id": "1356522628906750053", "author_name": "feilindeweiba", "author_bot": false, "content": "怎么感觉这套推图打boss有点难受啊，我4个满狂加满银钥能量进的第三章boss关死亡抵抗加复活两次才打赢，另一个号栗子，墨菲，艾瑞卡，灯塔没复活都能打赢，两个号都是24级", "timestamp": "2025-04-08T07:11:11.161000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1212339830835511347"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1358678163105779742", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1358673487673167942", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "兄弟们怎么配队", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1359081214128160842", "channel_id": "1358673487673167942", "type": 19, "author_id": "920561286578856007", "author_name": "be_queitplease", "author_bot": false, "content": "24和熔朵都很依赖手牌充狂\n偏偏这章的boss会溶解手牌\n所以到最后如果全部她们俩的牌都没了就很难打了", "timestamp": "2025-04-08T08:23:31.956000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1356522628906750053"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1359063007514066964", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1358673487673167942", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "兄弟们怎么配队", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1359081621105541262", "channel_id": "1358673487673167942", "type": 0, "author_id": "920561286578856007", "author_name": "be_queitplease", "author_bot": false, "content": "手牌变红色就代表打出去后会被溶解", "timestamp": "2025-04-08T08:25:08.987000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1358673487673167942", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "兄弟们怎么配队", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1359101439275827302", "channel_id": "1358673487673167942", "type": 19, "author_id": "1356522628906750053", "author_name": "feilindeweiba", "author_bot": false, "content": "这个我知道，手牌变红的时候我就只打了小骑士和拉蒙娜的打击和防御其他卡都没打，主要是boss血条好厚，24吃满加成也就打个两到三千的血，回狂的时候又顶不住伤害", "timestamp": "2025-04-08T09:43:54.007000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["920561286578856007"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1359081214128160842", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1358673487673167942", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "兄弟们怎么配队", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1359234789315575818", "channel_id": "1358673487673167942", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212339830835511347", "author_name": "muliupan", "author_bot": false, "content": "死亡抵抗正常，复活两次的话大概是命轮或抓造物或者输出方式的问题了。就算是御四家打希洛也不会复活的。  \n第一个融蚀阶段出掉防御牌来缩牌库保生存，第二个融蚀回合挂易伤，变成红温24，出三费再，拉蒙娜大招抽24三费，基本是可以秒的。\n带个r命轮狂乱，学着抓一下诅咒造物，勾爪白面黑烛死鸟什么的，都能很大提升伤害和运转。\n拉蒙娜三费要卖。\n24开荒的一个强势点是作为混沌c，可以更容易打无光之境四个本，提前突破等级限制，然后高等级碾主线。这点要利用好。", "timestamp": "2025-04-08T18:33:47.134000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1358673487673167942", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "兄弟们怎么配队", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
